        static final java.awt.Point HINT_CHECK_BUTTON_ON_PLAYING_SCREEN
        The center of the hint check button in the lower-right of the hit pop-up that appears for hints in the Angry Birds game for Google's Chrome web browser.

      • SKIP_ANIMATION_BUTTON

        static final java.awt.Point SKIP_ANIMATION_BUTTON
        The center of the skip animation button location in the Angry Birds game for Google's Chrome web browser. The animation that plays before level 1 loads can be skipped by pressing this location.

        Note: The animation does not appear in the SD mode.
